 Mi često imamo taj svjetovni pogled

1324
00:49:55,440 --> 00:49:56,120
 na te stvari,

1325
00:49:56,120 --> 00:49:57,900
 pa se onda nešto tu se malo gubimo.

1326
00:49:57,900 --> 00:49:59,920
 Ali Bog malo po malo mijenja naše srce,

1327
00:49:59,920 --> 00:50:00,980
 preobražava um,

1328
00:50:00,980 --> 00:50:02,400
 kako govori Pava u Rimljanima.

1329
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:05,060
 Ono, svaki dan malo preobrazba.

1330
00:50:05,060 --> 00:50:06,340
 Malo po malo,

1331
00:50:06,340 --> 00:50:08,120
 da što više On bude u nama.

1332
00:50:08,120 --> 00:50:09,000
 I jednostavno,

1333
00:50:09,000 --> 00:50:10,140
 to uvjerenje,

1334
00:50:10,140 --> 00:50:12,200
 taj odnos s njim nam pomaže,

1335
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:13,200
 aha, on ima plan.

1336
00:50:13,200 --> 00:50:14,400
 Ok, idem ga slušati.

1337
00:50:14,400 --> 00:50:14,980
 Šta sad?

1338
00:50:14,980 --> 00:50:16,000
 Kako sad napraviti?

1339
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:17,580
 Jer ne možeš ti sad sve to,

1340
00:50:17,580 --> 00:50:19,300
 on ti ne znaš šta te sve čeka na tom putu.

1341
00:50:19,300 --> 00:50:19,780
 Tako je.

1342
00:50:19,780 --> 00:50:20,920
 Nego, ajmo korak po korak.

1343
00:50:20,920 --> 00:50:21,720
 Prvi su, ne znam,

1344
00:50:21,720 --> 00:50:22,940
 važne su tu etape,

1345
00:50:22,940 --> 00:50:24,100
 nekake poglavlje.

1346
00:50:24,100 --> 00:50:24,440
 Ja kažem,

1347
00:50:24,440 --> 00:50:25,560
 prvo, jesi do na odluku

1348
00:50:25,560 --> 00:50:26,260
 da ideš u biznis?

1349
00:50:26,260 --> 00:50:27,520
 Aha, ok.

1350
00:50:27,520 --> 00:50:28,780
 Kad je ta odluka čvrsta,

1351
00:50:28,780 --> 00:50:29,540
 daj si vrijeme,

1352
00:50:29,540 --> 00:50:30,660
 nemoj preko noći.

1353
00:50:31,220 --> 00:50:32,280
 Nema preko noći ništa.

1354
00:50:32,280 --> 00:50:33,980
 Meni se to kuhalo,

1355
00:50:33,980 --> 00:50:34,880
 ja kažem, par godin.

1356
00:50:34,880 --> 00:50:36,500
 Tri godine, sigurno.

1357
00:50:36,500 --> 00:50:38,080
 I onda je došlo sad,

1358
00:50:38,080 --> 00:50:39,740
 kao da ti neki impuls unutra,

1359
00:50:39,740 --> 00:50:41,300
 aj sad taj korak više.

1360
00:50:41,300 --> 00:50:42,860
 I jednom ti nekako uspjevaš

1361
00:50:42,860 --> 00:50:43,880
 taj korak više naprijed.

1362
00:50:43,880 --> 00:50:44,380
 Odjednom,

1363
00:50:44,380 --> 00:50:45,700
 o, prostor se otvorio.

1364
00:50:45,700 --> 00:50:47,720
 Pa onda čekaš sedeći,

1365
00:50:47,720 --> 00:50:49,100
 aha, otvorio se i taj kredit

1366
00:50:49,100 --> 00:50:50,040
 kojeg nije bilo, ne znam,

1367
00:50:50,040 --> 00:50:50,640
 bila korona,

1368
00:50:50,640 --> 00:50:51,420
 ona nije bilo kredita,

1369
00:50:51,420 --> 00:50:51,840
 stogodno.

1370
00:50:51,840 --> 00:50:52,480
 I jednom,

1371
00:50:52,480 --> 00:50:53,680
 aha,

1372
00:50:53,680 --> 00:50:55,020
 i onda tebi se samo slaže kodskice.

1373
00:50:55,020 --> 00:50:56,160
 To je vrijeme,

1374
00:50:56,360 --> 00:50:56,600
 dobro,

1375
00:50:56,600 --> 00:50:57,160
 idemo.

1376
00:50:57,160 --> 00:50:58,700
 I malo pomali,

1377
00:50:58,700 --> 00:50:59,360
 Bog tako daje.

1378
00:50:59,360 --> 00:51:00,780
 I onda ti imaš jedno uvjerenje

1379
00:51:00,780 --> 00:51:01,240
 i mir.

1380
00:51:01,240 --> 00:51:01,440
 Znači,

1381
00:51:01,440 --> 00:51:02,300
 po mene je to važno,

1382
00:51:02,300 --> 00:51:03,540
 prvu tu etapu imat,

1383
00:51:03,540 --> 00:51:04,340
 jel tako,

1384
00:51:04,340 --> 00:51:04,800
 te stavio,

1385
00:51:04,800 --> 00:51:05,280
 okej,

1386
00:51:05,280 --> 00:51:06,440
 znam on koji je sljedeći korak,

1387
00:51:06,440 --> 00:51:07,900
 ali ga traži,

1388
00:51:07,900 --> 00:51:08,480
