1389
00:51:08,480 --> 00:51:09,080
 nemoj biti,

1390
00:51:09,080 --> 00:51:10,320
 nemoj misli da moraš znati.

1391
00:51:10,320 --> 00:51:11,000
 Misli,

1392
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:11,620
 nekad bojimo,

1393
00:51:11,620 --> 00:51:12,440
 pa kako ja sad,

1394
00:51:12,440 --> 00:51:13,880
 pa neku ja pričam o svojim slabosti,

1395
00:51:13,880 --> 00:51:15,360
 neku pričam da ima problema,

1396
00:51:15,360 --> 00:51:16,060
 da je teško.

1397
00:51:16,060 --> 00:51:16,840
 Pa ne,

1398
00:51:16,840 --> 00:51:17,340
 zašto ne?

1399
00:51:17,540 --> 00:51:20,700
 I zato ljudi se često mogu

1400
00:51:20,700 --> 00:51:21,540
 identificirati,

1401
00:51:21,540 --> 00:51:23,100
 kad neko u svjedočanstvima,

1402
00:51:23,100 --> 00:51:25,420
 kad priča o svojim slabostima,

1403
00:51:25,420 --> 00:51:26,720
 pogreškama i padovima,

1404
00:51:26,720 --> 00:51:27,620
 lakše njega sluša

1405
00:51:27,620 --> 00:51:29,580
 nego neko koji ti napiše

1406
00:51:29,580 --> 00:51:30,500
 kod da je svemu svet.

1407
00:51:30,500 --> 00:51:31,280
 Pa on su sori,

1408
00:51:31,280 --> 00:51:31,540
 prijatelj,

1409
00:51:31,540 --> 00:51:32,220
 ti izdaleko od me

1410
00:51:32,220 --> 00:51:33,880
 ne mogu se poistavijeti s tobom.

1411
00:51:33,880 --> 00:51:34,040
 Da,

1412
00:51:34,040 --> 00:51:34,860
 apsolutno.

1413
00:51:34,860 --> 00:51:35,300
 Tako da,

1414
00:51:35,300 --> 00:51:36,740
 to su prigovarali nekad

1415
00:51:36,740 --> 00:51:38,740
 našim hagiografijama,

1416
00:51:38,740 --> 00:51:40,760
 životopisi svetaca,

1417
00:51:40,760 --> 00:51:41,320
 nekad ispalo,

1418
00:51:41,320 --> 00:51:42,660
 ti sveci kod da nisu griješili,

1419
00:51:42,740 --> 00:51:43,800
 kod da su jem bili savršeni,

1420
00:51:43,800 --> 00:51:44,460
 pa čovjeće,

1421
00:51:44,460 --> 00:51:45,780
 samo iz deprimire kada ga čitam,

1422
00:51:45,780 --> 00:51:46,680
 ne mogu nikad to postići.

1423
00:51:46,680 --> 00:51:47,340
 Da, tako sam ja od toga,

1424
00:51:47,340 --> 00:51:48,340
 diću ja tu.

1425
00:51:48,340 --> 00:51:49,660
 A onda kad ti malo vidiš

1426
00:51:49,660 --> 00:51:51,560
 tu njegovu ljudsku dimenziju,

1427
00:51:51,560 --> 00:51:52,260
 odmah ti je lakše.

1428
00:51:52,260 --> 00:51:53,420
 Aha, pa mogu i ja,

1429
00:51:53,420 --> 00:51:54,380
 pa ohrabrite.

1430
00:51:54,380 --> 00:51:56,680
 E tako je ovdje nekako.

1431
00:51:56,680 --> 00:51:57,560
 Da,

1432
00:51:57,560 --> 00:51:59,180
 treba iskreno progovarati

1433
00:51:59,180 --> 00:52:00,700
 o tim težim početcima.

1434
00:52:00,700 --> 00:52:02,280
 Tako je,

1435
00:52:02,280 --> 00:52:02,580
 nekom,

1436
00:52:02,580 --> 00:52:03,020
 da,

1437
00:52:03,020 --> 00:52:04,360
 ljudima račile iskustva.

1438
00:52:04,360 --> 00:52:05,280
 Ima vjerojatno neko,

1439
00:52:05,400 --> 00:52:06,480
 ja znam ljudi koji su vrlo brzo

1440
00:52:06,480 --> 00:52:08,760
 takva narav posla,

1441
00:52:08,760 --> 00:52:09,500
 da su naprav jedan,

1442
00:52:09,500 --> 00:52:10,120
 dva dobra posla

1443
00:52:10,120 --> 00:52:11,280
 koji ih je katapultirao

1444
00:52:11,280 --> 00:52:11,960
 i da su, ne znam,

1445
00:52:11,960 --> 00:52:12,800
 prestali u financijama

1446
00:52:12,800 --> 00:52:13,820
 razmišljati nakon pola godine.

1447
00:52:13,820 --> 00:52:14,780
 Jako lijepo.

1448
00:52:14,780 --> 00:52:15,240
 Recimo.

1449
00:52:15,240 --> 00:52:15,900
 Ali su,

1450
00:52:15,900 --> 00:52:16,800
 kažem svako...

1451
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:17,400
 Ali rijetko.

1452
00:52:17,400 --> 00:52:19,020
 Ali svako ima put.

1453
00:52:19,020 --> 00:52:19,620
 Ja kažem,

1454
00:52:19,620 --> 00:52:20,360
 taj netko,

1455
00:52:20,360 --> 00:52:22,700
 Bog ima za njega njegov plan.

1456
00:52:22,700 --> 00:52:23,880
 On ga je možda lišio

1457
00:52:23,880 --> 00:52:24,780
 tih problema ovdje,

1458
00:52:24,780 --> 00:52:26,100
 ali će doći neki drugi problemi

1459
00:52:26,100 --> 00:52:26,540
 koji će mu trebati

1460
00:52:26,540 --> 00:52:28,820
 da izgradi neku drugu sferu,

1461
00:52:29,040 --> 00:52:30,340
 drugu dimenziju nečega

1462
00:52:30,340 --> 00:52:31,740
 zbog višeg cilja.

1463
00:52:31,740 --> 00:52:32,840
 Tako da...

1464
00:52:32,840 --> 00:52:33,460
 Da, da, da.

1465
00:52:33,460 --> 00:52:36,140
 Pitanje za kraj.

1466
00:52:36,140 --> 00:52:37,900
 Što sve nestaje

1467
00:52:37,900 --> 00:52:39,280
 i što se sve dobije

1468
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:40,800
 kad se u poduzetništu

1469
00:52:40,800 --> 00:52:41,880
 sve preda Bogu?

1470
00:52:41,880 --> 00:52:47,500
 Pa ono što sigurno nestaje

1471
00:52:47,500 --> 00:52:49,300
 je tjeskobna briga.

1472
00:52:49,300 --> 00:52:51,960
 Briga neće nestati,

1473
00:52:51,960 --> 00:52:53,760
 ali tjeskobna briga.

1474
00:52:53,760 --> 00:52:54,720
 Kad kažem,

1475
00:52:54,720 --> 00:52:56,180
 Božja riječ nam kaže

1476
00:52:56,180 --> 00:52:58,400
 nemojte se tjeskobno brinuti.

1477
00:52:58,680 --> 00:52:59,620
 iliko nemojte se brinuti.

1478
00:52:59,620 --> 00:53:00,800
 Pa ljudski se brinuti,

1479
00:53:00,800 --> 00:53:02,400
 pa moraš se pobrinuti za nešto,

1480
00:53:02,400 --> 00:53:04,280
 razmišljati, uključiti se do to.

1481
00:53:04,280 --> 00:53:05,640
 Ali nema ti je skobe,

1482
00:53:05,640 --> 00:53:07,580
 nema onog grča,

1483
00:53:07,580 --> 00:53:10,000
 one neke straha

1484
00:53:10,000 --> 00:53:11,040
 da te paralizira,

1485
00:53:11,040 --> 00:53:12,500
 kako to nekad zna bit.

1486
00:53:12,500 --> 00:53:14,160
 Ali to sigurno nije od Boga,

1487
00:53:14,160 --> 00:53:14,440
 ali da?

1488
00:53:14,440 --> 00:53:15,580
 To nije Božje.

1489
00:53:15,580 --> 00:53:16,780
 I to uvjerenje

1490
00:53:16,780 --> 00:53:17,840
 da je Bog s tobom,

1491
00:53:17,840 --> 00:53:20,860
 evo, to donosi taj mir.

1492
00:53:20,860 --> 00:53:22,820
 I to, jednostavno,

1493
00:53:22,820 --> 00:53:24,560
 znači nestaje taj strah,

1494
00:53:24,560 --> 00:53:25,460
 ta tje skoba,

1495
00:53:25,460 --> 00:53:28,660
 nestaje to da ti misli,

1496
00:53:28,680 --> 00:53:30,180
 ja to moram,

1497
00:53:30,180 --> 00:53:30,740
 sve ja to.

1498
00:53:30,740 --> 00:53:31,200
 Ne, ne, ne.

1499
00:53:31,200 --> 00:53:32,620
 Ima neko ko zna.

1500
00:53:32,620 --> 00:53:34,100
 I ja ne vidim plan,

1501
00:53:34,100 --> 00:53:34,800
 a on zna.

1502
00:53:34,800 --> 00:53:35,440
 Znači,

1503
00:53:35,440 --> 00:53:36,880
 dobit ćeš to jednu jasnoću,

1504
00:53:36,880 --> 00:53:38,860
 dobit ćeš u pravo vrijeme,

1505
00:53:38,860 --> 00:53:39,720
 na pravi način.

1506
00:53:39,720 --> 00:53:40,300
 Kaže,

1507
00:53:40,300 --> 00:53:41,900
 Bog nikad ne kasni,

1508
00:53:41,900 --> 00:53:43,780
 ali Bog nikad ni ne rani.

1509
00:53:43,780 --> 00:53:45,580
 On dođe u pravo vrijeme.

1510
00:53:45,580 --> 00:53:46,960
 Pa kako će biti,

1511
00:53:46,960 --> 00:53:47,820
 ako mi se to dogodi?

1512
00:53:47,820 --> 00:53:49,060
 E pa ako ti se to dogodi,

1513
00:53:49,060 --> 00:53:51,220
 Bog će dat tada šta je potrebno.

1514
00:53:51,220 --> 00:53:53,260
 Ja mam teško iskustvo,

1515
00:53:53,260 --> 00:53:53,860
 meni je otac umro

1516
00:53:53,860 --> 00:53:55,200
 kad sam imao nakon mog obraćanja

1517
00:53:55,200 --> 00:53:56,260
 na 2008. godine.

1518
00:53:56,260 --> 00:53:57,200
 Ja,

1519
00:53:57,200 --> 00:53:58,460
 to je bio moj najveći strah,

1520
00:53:58,460 --> 00:53:59,560
 šta će biti ako tata umre?

1521
00:53:59,560 --> 00:54:00,440
 Jednog dana,

1522
00:54:00,440 --> 00:54:01,540
 ili ja sam i ratno dijete,

1523
00:54:01,540 --> 00:54:02,460
 dobro se čečam rata,

1524
00:54:02,460 --> 00:54:02,980
 i podruma,

1525
00:54:02,980 --> 00:54:03,460
 i svega,

1526
00:54:03,460 --> 00:54:05,040
 i tata bio u vojci.

1527
00:54:05,040 --> 00:54:06,500
 I onda ti strahoji,

1528
00:54:06,500 --> 00:54:07,920
 šta tako tata pogine,

1529
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:08,260
 umre?

1530
00:54:08,260 --> 00:54:09,060
 I sad,

1531
00:54:09,060 --> 00:54:10,700
 nakon mog obraćanja,

1532
00:54:10,700 --> 00:54:11,360
 dogodilo se,

1533
00:54:11,360 --> 00:54:12,320
 došlo je do toga,

1534
00:54:12,380 --> 00:54:13,340
 da je tata preminuo

1535
00:54:13,340 --> 00:54:14,420
 nakon bolesti i tako,

1536
00:54:14,420 --> 00:54:16,520
 ali tad Bog meni dao

1537
00:54:16,520 --> 00:54:17,280
 nevratnu snagu.

1538
00:54:17,280 --> 00:54:18,660
 Ja to tada kao dijete

1539
00:54:18,660 --> 00:54:19,820
 nisam mogao niti zamisliti

1540
00:54:19,820 --> 00:54:20,520
 kako će to biti.

1541
00:54:20,520 --> 00:54:21,900
 Nemoguće.

1542
00:54:21,900 --> 00:54:22,420
 Jednostavno,

1543
00:54:22,420 --> 00:54:23,280
 ne možeš to zamisliti.

1544
00:54:23,280 --> 00:54:25,060
 To je najmeni teža stvar

1545
00:54:25,060 --> 00:54:25,660
 bila u životu.

1546
00:54:25,660 --> 00:54:26,500
 Međutim,

1547
00:54:26,500 --> 00:54:27,360
 kad je došlo to vrijeme,

1548
00:54:27,360 --> 00:54:28,480
 sam uspravio nikad veću

1549
00:54:28,480 --> 00:54:29,800
 Božju blizinu.

1550
00:54:29,800 --> 00:54:32,520
 E to je ono što mi dobijamo

1551
00:54:32,520 --> 00:54:33,320
 s odnosom s Bogom.

1552
00:54:33,320 --> 00:54:36,280
 On će reagirat kao otac

1553
00:54:36,280 --> 00:54:37,740
 u vrijeme kad to treba.

1554
00:54:37,740 --> 00:54:39,920
 A nameni da mu predajem.

1555
00:54:40,440 --> 00:54:41,340
 Naravno da ću ja puno puta

1556
00:54:41,340 --> 00:54:42,640
 u tom predavanju umirat.

1557
00:54:42,640 --> 00:54:43,760
 Misli da dio mene umire.

1558
00:54:43,760 --> 00:54:45,000
 Ja će umirat moj ego.

1559
00:54:45,000 --> 00:54:46,540
 Umirat će moja sebičnost,

1560
00:54:46,540 --> 00:54:47,940
 moja želja za kontrolom.

1561
00:54:47,940 --> 00:54:49,960
 Pa da, evo.

1562
00:54:49,960 --> 00:54:50,820
 Mislim mogli bi o tom.

1563
00:54:50,820 --> 00:54:52,720
 Bogu hvala pa nas oslobodi

1564
00:54:52,720 --> 00:54:54,160
 i sebičnosti,

1565
00:54:54,160 --> 00:54:54,980
 i koje dole,

1566
00:54:54,980 --> 00:54:56,300
 i oholosti.

1567
00:54:56,300 --> 00:54:57,080
 I kad se ne damo,

1568
00:54:57,080 --> 00:54:58,080
 onda malo te mora više zagrni.

1569
00:54:58,080 --> 00:54:59,260
 Onda malo više šarafi.

1570
00:54:59,260 --> 00:55:00,540
 Pa koji ti kadaš svoje dijete,

1571
00:55:00,540 --> 00:55:01,400
 pa ti je bi sve napravio

1572
00:55:01,400 --> 00:55:03,540
 da tvoje dijete bude čestit građanin,

1573
00:55:03,540 --> 00:55:04,460
